  - If `type === "percentage"`: `Math.round((cartTotal * value / 100) * 100) / 100`
  - If `type === "fixed"`: `Math.min(value, cartTotal)` (never negative total)
- Return `{ valid: true, type, value, discountAmount, finalTotal: cartTotal - discountAmount }`
- Do NOT increment `usedCount` here

